<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>News on Curious Electric</title><link>https://curious-electric.com/w/v2/news/</link><description>Recent content in News on Curious Electric</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en-us</language><lastBuildDate>Wed, 20 May 2026 11:00:00 +0200</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://curious-electric.com/w/v2/news/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>A browser-based editor for the Oberheim Matrix 1000</title><link>https://curious-electric.com/w/v2/news/oberheim-matrix1000/</link><pubDate>Wed, 20 May 2026 11:00:00 +0200</pubDate><guid>https://curious-electric.com/w/v2/news/oberheim-matrix1000/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;The Oberheim Matrix 1000 is a beloved analog synth from 1984 with a famously cryptic front panel — a handful of buttons for a hundred hidden parameters. So we gave it a proper editor that runs entirely in the browser.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Soft launch of mixxape!</title><link>https://curious-electric.com/w/v2/news/mixxape-1/</link><pubDate>Sat, 08 Feb 2025 11:00:00 +0200</pubDate><guid>https://curious-electric.com/w/v2/news/mixxape-1/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://mixxape.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;mixxape&lt;/a&gt; soft launches! Register with the newsletter to be part of the beta program.&lt;/p&gt;
